Version 0.1.4 (2018-04-03)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Fixed bugs in percent_bias, ape, and mape. These functions did not properly
handle negative values in the actual variable.

Version 0.1.3 (2017-10-21)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 * added new functions for computing accuracy, bias, percent bias, sum of squared errors, median absolute error, absolute percent error, mean absolute percent error, symmetric mean absolute percent error, and mean absolute scaled error.
 * restructured package into multiple files based on metric type.
 * fixed documentation bugs and made documentation more descriptive
 * fixed CRAN check errors
 * re-generated documentation and NAMESPACE using Roxygen2
 * added examples for all the functions
 * added a .Rbuildignore for ignoring the top level scripts
 * added Erin LeDell as a contributor
 * added Michael Frasco as an author and as the maintainer

Version 0.1.2 (2017-04-21)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 * package was migrated to “ORPHANED” status on CRAN
 * version number bumped automatically by CRAN

Version 0.1.1 (2012-06-19)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 * initial release
 * 16 evaluation metrics implemented with test cases
